Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.58,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I don't know why we're afraid of it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.04,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Never-ever felt it was today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:01.17,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I don't know what you pray for when you're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.26,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I don't know where we'll go tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.60,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Never-ever lose the way for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:10.39,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I'll know the reason that we are still here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.19,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Take me high
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.40,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Floating like a kite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.73,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Gently make me free
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.11,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Holding a thousand dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:25.16,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}流れる雲は ねぇ 何処へ行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.66,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}What do you want? What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:35.13,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}未来はそのまま太陽さえ飲み込んでしまうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.67,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}でも構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:43.76,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Cause we will be there again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:49.60,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I'll always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.58,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}不知为何我们害怕它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.04,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}从来没有像今天这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:01.17,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}不知当你孤独时在祈祷什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.26,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}不知明天我们将去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.60,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}从不曾迷失找寻你的路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:10.39,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}我知道为什么我们仍在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.19,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}把我带向高处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.40,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}像风筝一样飘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.73,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}温柔地给我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.11,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}抱有千万个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:25.16,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}流云 你将去向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.66,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}你想要什么 你看到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:35.13,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}未来甚至会就此吞没太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.67,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:43.76,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}因为我们会回归
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:49.60,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}永远在一起
