Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无从知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有这种终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 爆头 要爆头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁放那怪物上机的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第一夫人被咬了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统 请输入密码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都被<丧尸>咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经没有地方可降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们要趁现在摧毁所有用ICBM对准合众国的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:40.56,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}洲际弹道导弹 缩写ICBM 长程弹道导弹 该种导弹威力强大 常被设想成导致世界末日的核战争中使用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了下令启动国家非常事态作战规定666 Delta以外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有其他方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可履行我们对合众国宪法和人民的义务了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人…杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入密码…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神佑…美利坚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划啊划啊划啊划 划着小船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦～ 顺流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划啊划啊划啊划 划着小船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦～ 顺流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会唱英文版的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 唱来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划啊划啊划啊划 小船随流下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开开心心 开开心心 浮生似梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这次我们换歌词唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打打打手枪 射死它全家！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪啪啪啪啪！ 人生梦一场！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕太好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死肥宅 不要教坏小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道 原歌可是鹅妈妈童谣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多过完河了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是<丧尸> 还是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…冴子姐 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水 流出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 太阳都升起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是换身衣服比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室 帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放爱丽丝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小裤裤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说男生不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要换衣服 不准看这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.13,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希里爱丽丝 上小二了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:42.78,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是报纸记者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是「曾经是」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她爸爸说「等会能见到」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了朋友的衣服来 可以挑自己喜欢的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我能要这件夹克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这条裙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候履行我们的职责了 勇者小室！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是这么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 别老吠哦 吉克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,430)\fs20}Zeke
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉克？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉克这名字 是太平洋战争中美军对零战起的外号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零战？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 零式战斗机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 又小又敏捷 跟你很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是霰弹枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是对到头附近就能射中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不懂用法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是适合用铁棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就已经把子弹 也就是霰弹装上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要调整目标和瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能把头射飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你之前没练过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好瞄准靠近你的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹用完之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做 你就能打开枪膛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再像这样装子弹进去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般是四发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算上弹室里的一发的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有5发 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把枪 还有另一个特征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次讲那么多 我也不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不注意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且后座力还意外地强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真有个万一 我就用来当棍棒使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 有不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 挺适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会使这枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会叫平野教我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到危急情况还可以当长枪使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 可以可以 可以这样用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这枪还有军用的枪刀装置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开Hum-Vee上街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位男生 上街确保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Ma'am
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静香老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北非沙漠行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Rat Patrol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.96,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,美国早期系列剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是在突尼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎河…并没能挡住<丧尸>呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻也说了全世界都一样状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果警察还健存的话 一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 日本警察工作很热心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城家在东坂2丁目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最近的就是你家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去你家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多大机车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有得卖外国旧车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也会有军队不要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥你会这么清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到直升机或者飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明昨天还有那么多在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你有没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,察觉到啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自黎明以后都没遇见<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有<丧尸>！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离 右前方 300！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转右边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收…收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在那里转左 转左
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越靠近2丁目 数量就越多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有原因 肯定有原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接撞开它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快停车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人围了钢丝墙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把车身打横
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮胎被锁住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开刹车 稍稍踩一下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 前面 前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉滑套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着头附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 我明明瞄准了头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥只干掉了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为后座力 枪口跳动 子弹路径就上飘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像刺出去一样架枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对准<丧尸>的胸部附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像刺出去一样架枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对准胸部附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了一发以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按住扳机 只拉滑套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪口稍微移动一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙 你趁机救宫本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 用木刀来战的话 <丧尸>数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…能一起死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平野 这枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按掉扳机护笋前的杠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能解除安全装置了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再拉右侧的作动杆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不中 打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹匣没了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁给我递一个跟这个一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕太？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干翻它们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干翻它们全家！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死火后就点不着引擎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城 你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去捡小室的枪来用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹在你脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道怎么用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让人死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让任何人死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家就…近在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉克？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让爷们来装一下有型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模仿吉克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室 我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室 去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<丧尸>又往那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了来这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕太？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟吉克跳去钢丝后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家马上跟过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸快死的时候 表情跟小耕太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说了他没事 却死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝不要一个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟小耕太 孝哥哥 还有大姐姐们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 就地趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过后会把车回收过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像是消防队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们在危机关头救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是为了我女儿 还有她的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 是高城的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边的情况糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能期待救援到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迂回过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很熟这一带的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒岛学姐很强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室也很顽强的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明身处这种状况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却爽快极了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我 不断战斗 战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}先回去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我也是个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}啊 是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.96,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}小室一直都当我是女人看待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我也是个女人 喜欢上男人也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:32.51,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}不过 我从没表白过心意 因为觉得自己没有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}需要理由的话 我给你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}你会…负责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}冴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}求之不得！
